# Persona Intelligence Agent - Crontab Examples
# Date: 2026-03-25
#
# To install: crontab -e
# Then paste one of the examples below

# ==============================================================================
# Weekly Run - Every Tuesday at 2:00 AM
# ==============================================================================
0 2 * * 2 /Users/chris.sherman/persona_analysis/cron_template.sh

# ==============================================================================
# Weekly Run - Every Monday at 3:00 AM (alternative)
# ==============================================================================
# 0 3 * * 1 /Users/chris.sherman/persona_analysis/cron_template.sh

# ==============================================================================
# Bi-Weekly Run - Every other Monday at 2:00 AM
# ==============================================================================
# 0 2 * * 1 [ $(expr $(date +\%W) \% 2) -eq 0 ] && /Users/chris.sherman/persona_analysis/cron_template.sh

# ==============================================================================
# Monthly Run - First Monday of every month at 2:00 AM
# ==============================================================================
# 0 2 1-7 * 1 /Users/chris.sherman/persona_analysis/cron_template.sh

# ==============================================================================
# Daily Run - Every day at 2:00 AM (for testing)
# ==============================================================================
# 0 2 * * * /Users/chris.sherman/persona_analysis/cron_template.sh

# ==============================================================================
# Cron Format Reference:
# ==============================================================================
# ┌───────────── minute (0 - 59)
# │ ┌───────────── hour (0 - 23)
# │ │ ┌───────────── day of month (1 - 31)
# │ │ │ ┌───────────── month (1 - 12)
# │ │ │ │ ┌───────────── day of week (0 - 6) (Sunday to Saturday)
# │ │ │ │ │
# │ │ │ │ │
# * * * * * command to execute

# ==============================================================================
# Testing the Cron Job
# ==============================================================================
# Before adding to crontab, test the script manually:
#   cd /Users/chris.sherman/persona_analysis
#   ./cron_template.sh
#
# Check the log output:
#   tail -f logs/cron_run_*.log
#
# Verify outputs were created:
#   ls -l reports/
#   ls -l downstream_inputs/

# ==============================================================================
# Monitoring Cron Jobs
# ==============================================================================
# View active cron jobs:
#   crontab -l
#
# View cron logs (macOS):
#   grep CRON /var/log/system.log
#
# View cron logs (Linux):
#   grep CRON /var/log/syslog

# ==============================================================================
# Email Notifications
# ==============================================================================
# To receive email notifications when the job completes:
# 1. Set SEND_NOTIFICATIONS=true in cron_template.sh
# 2. Configure your system's mail command (e.g., postfix, sendmail)
# 3. Or use a cloud notification service (Slack, PagerDuty, etc.)

# ==============================================================================
# Troubleshooting
# ==============================================================================
# If cron job fails:
# 1. Check log files in logs/ directory
# 2. Verify .env file has correct credentials
# 3. Test script manually first
# 4. Ensure absolute paths are used (cron has minimal environment)
# 5. Check cron has permission to execute scripts
# 6. Verify Snowflake credentials haven't expired
